<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皮特开始讲述他的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我记得把你放在睡莲叶子上，然后突然你就不见了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以为你掉到水里去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一只叫布只的虫子把我抓走了。”拇指姑娘解释道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是没关系，接着讲你的故事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“睡莲叶子还挂在我的腿上。”皮特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我顺着河流一直找你，睡莲叶子卡在一些石头中间，”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我试着把叶子拉出来，但是没成功，我拉不出来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有好几天我都饿着肚子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“终于，几个朋友找到了我，他们把睡莲叶子啄成一块一块的，”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是没有人能把绳子解下来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接着就到了飞往南方的时候了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你怎么还在这儿？”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我走不了，我跟不上大家。”皮特说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我太虚弱了，感觉绳子很重。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的朋友们没有别的办法，只能离开我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有一段时间，我只能自己走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有一天，我的翅膀飞不动了，就掉到了地上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当我再次睁开眼的时候，就看见了你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我的错。”拇指姑娘大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，不是你的错。”皮特说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们是朋友，朋友就应该互相帮助，对吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以谢谢你帮助我，拇指姑娘。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不客气。”拇指姑娘不好意思地说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“既然你现在好多了，我们就得想个计划。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还是有点儿虚弱。”皮特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘指向他们头顶的洞：“我们能从那里出去吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皮特不确定地说：“嗯，我不知道……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的翅膀还能动吗？”拇指姑娘问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还是觉得冷。”皮特说，“但是我觉得我的翅膀还能动一点儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他们讨论计划的时候，有个人在盯着他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是格雷夫人。她到地道来寻找拇指姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拇指姑娘！你在这里干什么？”老鼠大叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从那只可怕的动物旁边走开！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别那么说皮特。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从地道的另一头走进来一个身影，是洛夫斯先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生什么事了？”他追问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还活着，洛夫斯先生。”格雷夫人喊道，“那只鸟儿没死！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”洛夫斯先生边说边摇头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，没关系，他不会活太久的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您这话是什么意思？”拇指姑娘问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“斯利姆就要来了。”洛夫斯先生边说边往上看，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我让他来这儿见我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，上方的地面开始震动，泥土掉在了他们的头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼来了，他用鼻子到处嗅了嗅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>